It is All All
A WONDERFUL low level magic weapon. (I was given a lambent stone at level 8
or so by someone who did not need one and went to trade it in for a Darkwood
Staff.)

Faesong, level 15 Songweaver of Solusek Ro, Mythical Alliance, Test
